Class DayOfYearSet

java.lang.Object
dayofyearset.DayOfYearSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class DayOfYearSet extends Object implements Cloneable
DayOfYearSet Class is a class keeps DayOfYear elements in the field array DayOfYear[] dates. DayOfYear is the inner class of its. It also has methods clone, equals, union, intersection, complement, setter and getters and other helper functions.
